title: Ebro In The Morning - Lizzo + Summer Jam Next Week
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Lizzo came through HOT 97 to drop off her brand new single "Rumors" featuring Cardi B!

Podcast Summer Jam Ticket WINNERS - @KristineAMiller & @DJnAsTyjAy - please DM @EbroInTheAm on Twitter!  

Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 8/13.

Ebro and the crew discuss vaccines, Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (34), and you find out who played themselves. 

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
